"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-07-14-year-old-olympian-reveals-unusual-gift-parents-winning-gold-21381143\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Arisa Trew,Australia's youngest Olympic champion inParis, revealed the unusual gift her parents are gifting her after she claimed skateboarding gold.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 5, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arisa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.352455485731463e-13, \"text\": \"Arisa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arisa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arisa\"}, {\"begin\": 11, \"end\": 20, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9755231472479227, \"rank\": 0.0095283784591679, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 14-year-old produced a superb display on four wheels to earn gold with a score of 93.18 asJapan's Cocona Hiraki andTeam GB's Sky Brown took silver and bronze respectively.\", \"from\": 151, \"to\": 326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 275, \"end\": 277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.970444842421683, \"rank\": 0.02572636554475798, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 280, \"end\": 289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sky Brown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the medal is not the only thing that the teenager will be rewarded with after revealing that her parents promised to get her a rather unusual winning gift: a pet duck.\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 504, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'My parents promised if I won the gold medal I would get a pet duck,' Trew told the Today show back in Australia.\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 609, \"end\": 618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9755231472479227, \"rank\": 0.0095283784591679, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics  'Because they are really cute, then I can take it on walks and take it to the skate park.\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 783, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'My parents definitely would not let me get a dog or a cat because we are travelling so much right now.\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 888, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'But I feel like a duck might be a little bit easier, and\\u2026 I do not know, I just want a duck.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 983, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It will just be in my yard and I will get a little pool thing for it.'\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 1056, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking more generally on her Olympic victory, she said: 'It was just crazy, and so exciting.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1152, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not believe it when I knew that I was the winner of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1226, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This being my first Olympics - it's just insane.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1275, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's super cool that I have won the gold medal - it's been a dream, I am so excited.\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1362, \"entities\": []}, {\"se